snippet.title: Good Doggo | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Available Now!
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/840060
Android: https://goo.gl/Rn5zA4
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/good-doggo/id1368798750?ls=1&mt=8
WebGL: https://cozygamepals.itch.io/good-doggo

Teach your good doggo to be the goodest doggo ever! Balance treats, toss them, and chomp them! The more you chomp the more you level up so you can chomp even harder!
